help-in-a-fast-changing-media-scene.jpg\",\"datePublished\":\"2023-07-23T03:05:00+00:00\",\"description\":\"Discover the potential career opportunities and earning potential that come with a master's degree in journalism. Explore high-paying job options in the field and take your career to new heights.\",\"breadcrumb\":{\"@id\":\"https:\\\/\\\/www.onlinemanipaladmission.in\\\/blogs\\\/can-a-masters-degree-in-journalism-get-you-high-paying-jobs#breadcrumb\"},\"inLanguage\":\"en-GB\",\"potentialAction\":[{\"@type\":\"ReadAction\",\"target\":[\"https:\\\/\\\/www.onlinemanipaladmission.in\\\/blogs\\\/can-a-masters-degree-in-journalism-get-you-high-paying-jobs\"]}]},{\"@type\":\"ImageObject\",\"inLanguage\":\"en-GB\",\"@id\":\"https:\\\/\\\/www.onlinemanipaladmission.in\\\/blogs\\\/can-a-masters-degree-in-journalism-get-you-high-paying-jobs#primaryimage\",\"url\":\"https:\\\/\\\/www.onlinemanipaladmission.in\\\/wp-content\\\/uploads\\\/2022\\\/07\\\/02.-How-a-degree-in-journalism-would-help-in-a-fast-changing-media-scene.jpg\",\"contentUrl\":\"https:\\\/\\\/www.onlinemanipaladmission.in\\\/wp-content\\\/uploads\\\/2022\\\/07\\\/02.-How-a-degree-in-journalism-would-help-in-a-fast-changing-media-scene.jpg\",\"width\":330,\"height\":150,\"caption\":\"Careers after MA JMC\"},{\"@type\":\"BreadcrumbList\",\"@id\":\"https:\\\/\\\/www.onlinemanipaladmission.in\\\/blogs\\\/can-a-masters-degree-in-journalism-get-you-high-paying-jobs#breadcrumb\",\"itemListElement\":[{\"@type\":\"ListItem\",\"position\":1,\"name\":\"Home\",\"item\":\"https:\\\/\\\/www.onlinemanipaladmission.in\\\/\"},{\"@type\":\"ListItem\",\"position\":2,\"name\":\"Can a master&#8217;s degree in journalism get you high-paying jobs?\"}]},{\"@type\":\"WebSite\",\"@id\":\"https:\\\/\\\/www.onlinemanipaladmission.in\\\/#website\",\"url\":\"https:\\\/\\\/www.onlinemanipaladmission.in\\\/\",\"name\":\"Online Manipal\",\"description\":\"Online Manipal\",\"publisher\":{\"@id\":\"https:\\\/\\\/www.onlinemanipaladmission.i